{"tid":108750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警犬隊警車山頂撞壆　車長撞傷頭手腳","createTime":"2017-02-05T13:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T00:28:04.000Z","uid":32407,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f7f147a7cfbb08dba2df54c5fedfe93dc7d21a","tid":108750,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:15:35.000Z","msg":"凌晨零時36分，警犬隊（PDU）一輛運載警犬的警車，沿山頂道上斜行駛，途至山頂道92號對出時，疑因天雨路滑失控撞向左邊路旁石壆，車頭防撞欄損毀。警車上的警犬無恙，而駕駛警車的警員頭、手及腳部撞傷，自行報案，清醒送瑪麗醫院治理，車上警犬則由另一輛警車運走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/371156/xlarge/e984cbae392b4f71b21458a2ab1fde0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F371156%2Fxlarge%2Fe984cbae392b4f71b21458a2ab1fde0e.jpg&h=a3d16d8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n運警犬警車車頭損毀。（陳永武攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/371157/xlarge/d9c418650e0014f631dbf131775d26fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F371157%2Fxlarge%2Fd9c418650e0014f631dbf131775d26fe.jpg&h=f81fe9e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受傷警員送院治理。（陳永武攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/69626/%E8%AD%A6%E7%8A%AC%E9%9A%8A%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A%E5%B1%B1%E9%A0%82%E6%92%9E%E5%A3%86-%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E6%92%9E%E5%82%B7%E9%A0%AD%E6%89%8B%E8%85%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F69626%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%258A%25AC%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E9%25A0%2582%25E6%2592%259E%25E5%25A3%2586-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%2592%259E%25E5%2582%25B7%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2585%25B3&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=7a70c795\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/69626/%E8%AD%A6%E7%8A%AC%E9%9A%8A%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A%E5%B1%B1%E9%A0%82%E6%92%9E%E5%A3%86-%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E6%92%9E%E5%82%B7%E9%A0%AD%E6%89%8B%E8%85%B3</a>"},{"pid":"d355f90414317b58447c